    public static interface I18NResourceBundleBuilder.LastStep
    The last step in this fluent builder.

    With the option build() the developer completes the previsous configuration steps from the ResourceBundle and the different Locales.

    • Method Detail

      • build

        void build()
        Completes the previous configuration steps from the ResourceBundle and the different Locales in this fluent builder.

        At last it will be checked if a ResourceBundle with the predefined parameters baseBundleName and actualLocale can be loaded.
        If not a MissingResourceException will be thrown.

        Since:
        0.1.0-PRERELEASE
        See Also:
        Locale, MissingResourceException, ResourceBundle
